'''Chusé Raúl Usón Serrano''' ('''Jusep Raül Uson''' in [[Sociedat de Lingüistica Aragonesa|SLA orthography]]), born in 1966 in [[Zaragoza]], is a publisher and a Spanish writer in the [[Aragonese language]].

